      "title": "The office",
      "quick_hits": "This is where your adventure begins! Grab a park map inside if you want one.",
      "directions_text": ""
    },
    {
      "tour_id": "1",
      "stop_number": "0.5",
      "type": "Directions",
      "psbp_id": "",
      "title": "",
      "quick_hits": "",
      "directions_text": "Walk out the office door and head straight down the path. Look for the tree with the spiky green trunk — you can't miss it!"
    },
    {
      "tour_id": "1",
      "stop_number": "1",
      "type": "Stop",
      "psbp_id": "PSBP-00002",
      "title": "jljljljlkj ",
      "quick_hits": "Touch the spikes on the trunk — but carefully! | The trunk is green because it does photosynthesis like a leaf | Produces fluffy cotton-like fiber inside its seed pods",
      "directions_text": ""
    },
    {
      "tour_id": "1",
      "stop_number": "1.5",
      "type": "Directions",
      "psbp_id": "",
      "title": "",
      "quick_hits": "",
      "directions_text": "Keep walking past the spiky tree. On your right you'll see a really big pond. Count how many turtles you can spot! Now look for a tree with enormous leaves."
    },
    {
      "tour_id": "1",
      "stop_number": "2",
      "type": "Stop",
      "psbp_id": "PSBP-00123",
      "title": "rrerererer",
      "quick_hits": "The leaves are as big as a dinner plate — bigger than your head! | Used to build ships and fancy furniture | Young leaves can be reddish-purple",
      "directions_text": ""
    },
    {
      "tour_id": "1",
      "stop_number": "2.5",
      "type": "Directions",
      "psbp_id": "",
      "title": "",
      "quick_hits": "",
      "directions_text": "Turn left and follow the path along the pond. Can you hear any birds? Look for a tree with fruit that looks like a giant green brain."
    },
    {
      "tour_id": "1",
      "stop_number": "3",
      "type": "Stop",
      "psbp_id": "PSBP-00099",
      "title": "jljlkjljlk",
      "quick_hits": "The biggest fruit that grows on a tree — they can weigh 80 pounds! | The bumpy skin is actually made of tiny hexagons | Smells sweet and tastes like a mix of banana and pineapple",
      "directions_text": ""
    },
